{"tid":1902944,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果有人覺得自己開始對抗爭嘅熱情減退請入一入黎","createTime":"2020-02-28T15:45:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T17:18:45.000Z","uid":350697,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"52c28ff501cd16b8b6fefc6d66cdb714c0b707d1","tid":1902944,"uid":350697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:45:24.000Z","msg":"p牌仔，單純想講一講自己感受出黎<br />\n<br />\n首先，我覺得一個人長期保持憤怒係無可能<br />\n大家都知係長期戰，而所謂熱情減退只係大家習慣左<br />\n但習慣係一樣好正常嘅事<br />\n我哋要諗嘅係點樣保持自己嘅意識形態長期keep落去<br />\n我哋已經有黃色經濟圈，有文宣，有唔同手段去抗爭<br />\n我哋已經係自己心中埋下左種子<br />\n而點樣去keep住灌溉佢，我覺得和理非平時多啲聽歌係其中一個方法<br />\nkeep住去提醒自己，香港有發生個啲咁嘅事<br />\n唔好因為習慣，麻木而唔好理會<br />\n到有其他事發生嘅時候，政府都難啲去分散你地注意力<br />\n例如因派錢分散你地注意力or自己友做錯事而去過份指責佢地，導致大家一時唔記得左敵人都做緊野<br />\n而忘記香港之前咁多個月發生嘅野<br />\n當大家覺得有時over左嘅時候<br />\n希望都可以聽返依首歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZQGR-RvFONw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZQGR-RvFONw&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJCHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=c7265b1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZQGR-RvFONw</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"ce891ddbf0d7b9487a67a773997322ee4454a27f","tid":1902944,"uid":350697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:47:42.000Z","msg":"p牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3168714439d2ea8fd42db6d6c7ca098b6105f8a9","tid":1902944,"uid":350697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:52:07.000Z","msg":"有無人幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"765e61e0ee40bf83514ca47a7387f36d425ed91e","tid":1902944,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:52:42.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"0971c033e7787e8354c0b8acffbbe36b833dc336","tid":1902944,"uid":350697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:57:30.000Z","msg":"覺得自己熱情減退係因為忘記<br />\n其實好正常，但有方法去提醒自己<br />\n希望大家睇一睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0927db3d75df79dd1016b2b6047a480226e7cec5","tid":1902944,"uid":350697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"765e61e0ee40bf83514ca47a7387f36d425ed91e","tid":1902944,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:52:42.000Z","msg":"Up"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:58:03.000Z","msg":"感謝推po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72119d8db600b71e6af5bb9486c79327af6e1a3","tid":1902944,"uid":308377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T16:02:45.000Z","msg":"P TUI<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e31bd163967dc3dfebb166e82e797a43a8979623","tid":1902944,"uid":350697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c72119d8db600b71e6af5bb9486c79327af6e1a3","tid":1902944,"uid":308377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T16:02:45.000Z","msg":"P TUI<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T16:03:54.000Z","msg":"雖然推唔到但感謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef56e4cf23a375c9a3e306c005c1f6932970ee5","tid":1902944,"uid":20363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T16:08:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53124991a13ee50dde1042ac09beb61117243945","tid":1902944,"uid":310282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T16:09:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7557f1f9a8a54c4e2606c90aaddaa58f21bc81e4","tid":1902944,"uid":350697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T16:09:52.000Z","msg":"點解咁快有人負皮我<br />\n歡迎討論"},{"pid":"8da54a105306909a7843493f42d761032ad8c08c","tid":1902944,"uid":292151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T16:09:54.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb2c848fdf7e